---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base>
  <Fragment slot="head-title">Manifesto | Archive of the Untamed</Fragment>

  <header>
    <h1>ARCHIVE OF THE UNTAMED :: MANIFESTO</h1>
  </header>

  <pre id="manifesto-terminal"></pre>

  <script is:inline>
    const text = `ARCHIVE_OF_THE_UNTAMED :: MANIFESTO

This is not an archive_of_the_past.
This is not a [NEUTRAL_REPOSITORY].

It is a {LIVING_SYSTEM} ⭐
made_of(gestures, roots, soil, stories)

An_interface between [BODY] and [ENVIRONMENT],
between {RESISTANCE} and {MEMORY} ⭐

It archives what_escapes,
what_overgrows,
what_exceeds(protocols_of_control)

The {WILD} is not the other.
It is the force_that_resists_capture ⭐
that grows_in(cracks_of_domination)

Archive_of_the_Untamed is a TOOL_for:
- imagining_otherwise()
- reclaiming_space()
- documenting(the_unarchivable)

:: WILDNESS = data :: FEELING = evidence :: DISORDER = method`;

    const el = document.getElementById("manifesto-terminal");
    let i = 0;
    function type() {
      if (i < text.length) {
        el.textContent += text.charAt(i++);
        requestAnimationFrame(() => setTimeout(type, 10));
      }
    }
    type();
  </script>
</Base>
